title: The amenity package includes a spacious 24-hour, club-quality fitness
posting_body: ['$%#%Modera Edgewater offers the kinds of advantages many dream about, but only few have the privilege of experiencing.', 'The amenity package includes a spacious 24-hour, club-quality fitness center and separate studio, steam room and sauna, sparkling outdoor pool, including a rooftop pool deck with scenic views, private, controlled access garage parking, an expansive clubhouse with a movie lounge, and a business center with private offices and conference rooms.$%#', '#$%If you have been denied an application for lease in the past due to bad credit or your background, please call me or text me', 'show contact info', ', I will get you approved!!', 'Self-employed, bad credit, no problem.', 'Text me, I respond immediately and have tons of inventory!', 'WE ARE ESSENTIAL BUSINESS FOR COVI19, WE ARE ALWAYS OPEN', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'Andy Zamudio', 'show contact info', 'We accept deposits with credit card if you are short of cash we help with that, we are the only company that accepts credit cards for deposits , zelle, cash app, paypal venmo payments accepted!!!', 'Aceptamos los depositos con tarjeta de credito sinud esta corto de cash, somos la unica compañia que lo acepta en Florida, zelle, cash app, paypal ,venmo.']
